use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 16, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104whw1665702766757.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/whw1665702766757.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/whw1665702766757.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"whw1665702766757\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      dump\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"whw1665702766757__dump_66060\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Dump ProcScript instructions to the screen or message frame.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"whw1665702766757__topic_d19241e1_d19242e1_d19243e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"whw1665702766757__p_d19244e1_d19245e1_d19246e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">DUMP</code> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Module</var>} | <code class=\"ph codeph\">/all</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"whw1665702766757__topic_d13852e1_d13853e1_d13854e1_d13855e1_d13856e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d673322e68\">\n                        \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"whw1665702766757__li_d9443e1_d9444e1_d9445e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Module</var>—name of a global ProcScript, function, operation, or an\n               internally-generated label. If omitted, the current module is assumed. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"whw1665702766757__li_d9446e1_d9447e1_d9448e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">/all</code>—dump all modules of the\n               current component. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"whw1665702766757__topic_d13857e1_d13858e1_d13859e1_d13860e1_d13861e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d673322e88\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"whw1665702766757__p_d19253e1_d19254e1_d19255e1\">Dump the statements of the ProcScript module to the message frame (if <code class=\"ph codeph\">putmess on</code> has been used previously) or to the screen (<code class=\"ph codeph\">putmess off</code>).</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"whw1665702766757__section_mbn_dhb_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d673322e103\">Example: </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"whw1665702766757__pre_acj_2hb_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">dump gp_store\ndump/all\ndump</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hdt1665702766826.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>putmess</a><p>Specify the destination of the message frame output.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616723\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616723\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "dump Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 16, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 dump Dump ProcScript instructions to the screen or message frame. DUMP { Module } | /all Arguments Module —name of a global ProcScript, function, operation, or an internally-generated label. If omitted, the current module is assumed. /all —dump all modules of the current component. Description Dump the statements of the ProcScript module to the message frame (if putmess on has been used previously) or to the screen ( putmess off ). Example: dump gp_store dump/all dump Copy Related Links putmess Specify the destination of the message frame output. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}